1
00:00:00,060 --> 00:00:05,100
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,100 --> 00:00:10,220
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,220 --> 00:00:15,380
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,380 --> 00:00:22,780
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,620 --> 00:00:30,740
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,740 --> 00:00:35,620
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,860 --> 00:00:40,300
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,860 --> 00:00:49,660
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,980 --> 00:00:54,300
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:59,420
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,740 --> 00:01:03,420
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,420 --> 00:01:06,020
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,500 --> 00:01:10,140
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:14,740
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,580 --> 00:01:20,100
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,140 --> 00:01:23,900
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,900 --> 00:01:26,500
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,780 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 44 =

20
00:01:34,140 --> 00:01:35,420
The misbehaved

21
00:01:35,420 --> 00:01:36,460
are all pardoned.

22
00:01:37,300 --> 00:01:39,140
The drunk couldn’t think straight.

23
00:01:42,700 --> 00:01:43,500
Your Majesty...

24
00:01:50,420 --> 00:01:51,380
What else?

25
00:01:54,580 --> 00:01:59,100
They’re all court scholars

26
00:01:59,540 --> 00:02:02,940
who’re self-claimed gentlemen.

27
00:02:03,820 --> 00:02:05,780
Yet they hired showgirls

28
00:02:06,300 --> 00:02:08,660
to sing and dance erotic pieces

29
00:02:08,900 --> 00:02:10,620
while flirting with them.

30
00:02:10,620 --> 00:02:11,860
That’s unacceptable!

31
00:02:13,340 --> 00:02:14,660
More importantly,

32
00:02:15,140 --> 00:02:17,340
Jiang Xiufu, Zhou Yanjun and a few others

33
00:02:18,060 --> 00:02:19,260
are still in mourning for their families.

34
00:02:19,500 --> 00:02:21,020
Wang Yirou said in his poem,

35
00:02:23,860 --> 00:02:27,260
“I’ll send an emperor to support him.

36
00:02:27,420 --> 00:02:29,660
I’ll enslave even Duke of Zhou and Confucius”.

37
00:02:29,660 --> 00:02:31,740
They all guffawed at it.

38
00:02:32,100 --> 00:02:32,860
How rude!

39
00:02:34,460 --> 00:02:35,900
Those at the banquet yesterday

40
00:02:36,540 --> 00:02:37,940
are scholars with ranks

41
00:02:38,340 --> 00:02:40,500
who are models of morality in the public eye.

42
00:02:41,540 --> 00:02:42,340
But what did they do?

43
00:02:43,220 --> 00:02:46,100
They indulged themselves in obscene pleasure.

44
00:02:46,580 --> 00:02:47,980
In Wang Yirou’s poem,

45
00:02:48,220 --> 00:02:50,140
the emperor and the sages

46
00:02:50,340 --> 00:02:52,380
were degraded to slaves.

47
00:02:53,700 --> 00:02:55,340
Does he have any respect

48
00:02:55,460 --> 00:02:57,500
for his father, teachers

49
00:02:58,100 --> 00:02:59,940
and Confucius?

50
00:03:00,420 --> 00:03:03,060
He’s...he’s treacherous!

51
00:03:05,860 --> 00:03:06,540
Your Majesty.

52
00:03:07,700 --> 00:03:09,140
That poem is disrespectful.

53
00:03:09,540 --> 00:03:10,940
Wang Yirou is always wild

54
00:03:11,260 --> 00:03:12,420
and should be punished.

55
00:03:13,620 --> 00:03:16,020
But calling a conceited talent

56
00:03:16,220 --> 00:03:18,700
treacherous simply based on a few drunk words

57
00:03:19,620 --> 00:03:21,820
is too much.

58
00:03:22,980 --> 00:03:24,820
Our state is peaceful

59
00:03:25,500 --> 00:03:27,860
and prosperous. There’s no treachery.

60
00:03:33,340 --> 00:03:34,100
Your Majesty.

61
00:03:34,340 --> 00:03:36,140
Deputy Censor Wang Gongchen

62
00:03:36,180 --> 00:03:38,460
requests to be summoned.

63
00:03:39,180 --> 00:03:40,260
He says

64
00:03:40,460 --> 00:03:42,060
he has key evidence

65
00:03:42,300 --> 00:03:44,860
against scholars who hired harlots

66
00:03:45,020 --> 00:03:47,220
and committed sacrilege yesterday.

67
00:03:50,660 --> 00:03:51,820
Your Majesty.

68
00:03:53,580 --> 00:03:55,780
Su Shunqin, Wang Yirou and the others

69
00:03:55,780 --> 00:03:57,380
not only showed no respect for the law and order,

70
00:03:57,380 --> 00:03:58,340
uttered disrespectful remarks,

71
00:03:58,900 --> 00:04:01,740
but squandered public money on entertainment.

72
00:04:02,660 --> 00:04:06,220
As the head of the Bureau of Reports,

73
00:04:06,580 --> 00:04:08,940
Su Shunqin is guilty of embezzlement

74
00:04:09,100 --> 00:04:12,340
and shall be beheaded.

75
00:04:18,140 --> 00:04:20,540
= Wu Yu, courtesy name Chunqing =
According to my knowledge,

76
00:04:20,820 --> 00:04:22,660
paper the Bureau of Reports needs

77
00:04:22,660 --> 00:04:24,500
for letters and proposals is uncountable.

78
00:04:25,140 --> 00:04:25,900
Chiefs before Su Shunqin

79
00:04:25,900 --> 00:04:27,500
all sold the old paper

80
00:04:27,700 --> 00:04:28,980
in exchange for money.

81
00:04:29,540 --> 00:04:32,060
Other than offering sacrifices to Heaven,

82
00:04:32,220 --> 00:04:33,140
if there’s money left,

83
00:04:33,420 --> 00:04:34,620
they’ll use it

84
00:04:34,620 --> 00:04:36,140
on meals and entertainment.

85
00:04:36,820 --> 00:04:39,420
Su Shunqin didn’t start it

86
00:04:39,740 --> 00:04:40,820
but only followed the tradition.

87
00:04:42,580 --> 00:04:44,220
Embezzlement and corruption

88
00:04:44,580 --> 00:04:45,940
also have a long-standing history.

89
00:04:46,380 --> 00:04:48,060
It happens in every reign and dynasty.

90
00:04:48,540 --> 00:04:50,420
None of the corrupted officials started it.

91
00:04:51,140 --> 00:04:52,140
According to you,

92
00:04:52,700 --> 00:04:53,820
they also followed in others’ steps.

93
00:04:54,420 --> 00:04:56,060
In that case,

94
00:04:56,500 --> 00:04:58,100
can all the corrupted be pardoned

95
00:04:58,220 --> 00:05:00,420
since their actions

96
00:05:00,980 --> 00:05:03,020
are precedented?

97
00:05:05,620 --> 00:05:06,340
Your Majesty.

98
00:05:07,020 --> 00:05:08,980
Embezzlement has existed since ancient times.

99
00:05:09,460 --> 00:05:11,780
The excess of officials is seen in every dynasty.

100
00:05:12,500 --> 00:05:14,500
Fan Zhongyan, Ouyang Xiu and Han Qi

101
00:05:14,780 --> 00:05:16,020
enforced harsh and oppressive rules

102
00:05:16,540 --> 00:05:18,460
on officials in the name of reform.

103
00:05:18,660 --> 00:05:21,020
Their careers are destroyed.

104
00:05:21,020 --> 00:05:23,300
The court is shaken.

105
00:05:24,100 --> 00:05:25,620
Su Shunqin and Wang Yirou

106
00:05:25,620 --> 00:05:28,060
sought pleasure with public funds

107
00:05:28,340 --> 00:05:30,340
but criticized state policies

108
00:05:30,860 --> 00:05:32,540
for Fan Zhongyan and Fu Bi?

109
00:05:33,300 --> 00:05:34,340
As benighted as I am,

110
00:05:34,660 --> 00:05:36,940
I studied the classics hard

111
00:05:37,420 --> 00:05:39,300
and was appointed the principal graduate
by Your Majesty.

112
00:05:40,300 --> 00:05:42,340
But now, I’m wondering

113
00:05:42,460 --> 00:05:45,460
where justice is.

114
00:05:52,780 --> 00:05:54,820
We’re having a routine discussion.

115
00:05:56,420 --> 00:05:58,660
This isn’t a life-or-death moment.

116
00:06:01,500 --> 00:06:02,380
You may rise.

117
00:06:17,020 --> 00:06:21,100
Didn’t Fan Zhongyan recommend Wang Yirou

118
00:06:21,100 --> 00:06:23,380
to be a Corrector?

119
00:06:27,500 --> 00:06:29,220
He once submitted a proposal

120
00:06:29,340 --> 00:06:30,660
to discuss the construction of Shuiluo City

121
00:06:31,700 --> 00:06:34,580
where he obviously took Yin Zhu’s side

122
00:06:34,980 --> 00:06:36,700
and defamed General Liu Hu,

123
00:06:37,100 --> 00:06:39,060
claiming that he should be killed for defiance,

124
00:06:39,980 --> 00:06:40,980
didn’t he?

125
00:06:42,460 --> 00:06:43,620
Is he

126
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:46,420
also a member

127
00:06:46,420 --> 00:06:48,260
of the Clique of Gentlemen

128
00:06:48,820 --> 00:06:52,380
that Ouyang Xiu described in his article?

129
00:07:06,420 --> 00:07:07,540
There’s a fishing rod for you.

130
00:07:07,700 --> 00:07:08,660
Choose the bait you like.

131
00:07:12,860 --> 00:07:14,100
Thank you, Your Majesty.

132
00:07:33,100 --> 00:07:36,260
Are you leaving tomorrow?

133
00:07:38,380 --> 00:07:39,140
Yes.

134
00:07:41,700 --> 00:07:43,460
“Travel to Yangzhou in the misty flowery March”.

135
00:07:45,020 --> 00:07:46,180
Enjoy your trip.

136
00:07:50,540 --> 00:07:51,540
I dare not.

137
00:07:54,540 --> 00:07:57,980
Are you too angry to enjoy the view?

138
00:08:02,900 --> 00:08:05,900
I failed in my duty and deserve no relaxation.

139
00:08:14,220 --> 00:08:15,740
You completed your task.

140
00:08:16,460 --> 00:08:17,500
It wasn’t too remarkable an achievement

141
00:08:17,500 --> 00:08:18,580
but the result was acceptable.

142
00:08:19,820 --> 00:08:20,820
Who said you failed?

143
00:08:29,900 --> 00:08:30,820
The only problem is

144
00:08:30,940 --> 00:08:32,420
your talent isn’t enough

145
00:08:33,020 --> 00:08:35,740
to support you to be a Prime Minister.

146
00:08:50,060 --> 00:08:50,980
Over the past two years,

147
00:08:51,540 --> 00:08:53,660
when Fan Zhongyan and I were in charge,

148
00:08:54,340 --> 00:08:55,460
I was cautious

149
00:08:56,100 --> 00:08:57,420
but still made tons of mistakes.

150
00:08:58,260 --> 00:08:59,100
Looking back,

151
00:08:59,820 --> 00:09:01,260
I know I’m too reckless and stubborn

152
00:09:01,860 --> 00:09:03,260
to be a Prime Minister,

153
00:09:04,140 --> 00:09:05,260
so I bear no resentment

154
00:09:05,700 --> 00:09:07,020
that I’m transferred out of the Capital.

155
00:09:08,340 --> 00:09:11,660
But with all due respect,

156
00:09:12,820 --> 00:09:14,260
I still have two things to report.

157
00:09:17,220 --> 00:09:18,540
Defend for Su Shunqin

158
00:09:19,500 --> 00:09:20,780
and the reform.

159
00:09:26,380 --> 00:09:27,740
Not wise at all.

160
00:09:38,340 --> 00:09:39,620
Guards in the palace and the Agency

161
00:09:39,620 --> 00:09:41,740
have been looking for the missing maid for a year.

162
00:09:42,100 --> 00:09:44,700
Who knew she’d be here?

163
00:09:46,180 --> 00:09:48,540
How...how did this happen?

164
00:09:49,140 --> 00:09:50,180
My adopted mother brought her back

165
00:09:50,180 --> 00:09:51,340
from the market.

166
00:09:51,340 --> 00:09:53,380
You didn’t even ask her about her background

167
00:09:54,540 --> 00:09:55,460
before taking her in?

168
00:09:56,940 --> 00:09:59,340
She couldn’t speak or read.

169
00:09:59,820 --> 00:10:02,300
That’s why she pretended to be mute.

170
00:10:07,300 --> 00:10:08,460
I’m here already.

171
00:10:09,540 --> 00:10:10,500
If you

172
00:10:10,500 --> 00:10:12,420
tell me the truth

173
00:10:13,500 --> 00:10:15,540
and your action is forgivable,

174
00:10:16,060 --> 00:10:17,580
I’ll ask for leniency for you.

175
00:10:22,540 --> 00:10:23,340
Or

176
00:10:24,180 --> 00:10:25,140
I should hand you

177
00:10:25,140 --> 00:10:26,220
to Deputy Officer Yang directly.

178
00:10:26,980 --> 00:10:27,820
This case

179
00:10:28,420 --> 00:10:31,180
isn’t my business anyway.

180
00:10:32,580 --> 00:10:35,780
= Bitao =

181
00:10:35,780 --> 00:10:36,620
Don’t!

182
00:10:43,940 --> 00:10:47,220
Is Su Shunqin’s punishment too severe to you?

183
00:10:50,260 --> 00:10:50,980
I think

184
00:10:51,860 --> 00:10:52,980
Su Shunqin and Wang Yirou

185
00:10:53,260 --> 00:10:54,380
only did what their predecessors do

186
00:10:54,820 --> 00:10:55,620
by using the money left

187
00:10:55,620 --> 00:10:56,940
after offering sacrifices to heaven

188
00:10:56,940 --> 00:10:57,700
to buy food and liquor

189
00:10:57,860 --> 00:10:59,380
and share them with colleagues.

190
00:11:00,060 --> 00:11:00,980
The tradition is flawed

191
00:11:01,260 --> 00:11:03,140
but it’s far from embezzlement.

192
00:11:04,340 --> 00:11:06,020
As for disrespectful remarks

193
00:11:06,020 --> 00:11:06,700
they made about the emperor and the sages,

194
00:11:06,940 --> 00:11:08,260
those were drunk words.

195
00:11:09,220 --> 00:11:09,980
People who accused them

196
00:11:09,980 --> 00:11:11,460
of treachery

197
00:11:11,860 --> 00:11:13,100
are ill-intentioned.

198
00:11:13,420 --> 00:11:15,820
They should be eliminated for slander.

199
00:11:27,580 --> 00:11:28,500
Clearly, you’ve decided

200
00:11:28,500 --> 00:11:30,140
to lay out your honest thoughts

201
00:11:30,260 --> 00:11:31,620
before me at all costs.

202
00:11:32,980 --> 00:11:34,420
Why don’t you

203
00:11:34,420 --> 00:11:35,100
get them all out?

204
00:11:42,460 --> 00:11:43,940
Su Shunqin and Wang Yirou

205
00:11:44,060 --> 00:11:46,060
did give others leverage to be used against them.

206
00:11:46,660 --> 00:11:48,180
But dragging Fan Zhongyan,

207
00:11:48,180 --> 00:11:49,060
who appreciated Wang Yirou’s talent

208
00:11:49,060 --> 00:11:50,780
and recommended him for the post a year ago,

209
00:11:51,340 --> 00:11:53,340
and Su Shunqin’s father-in-law, into this case

210
00:11:53,980 --> 00:11:55,780
is farfetched, isn’t it?

211
00:11:56,620 --> 00:11:57,500
Not to mention

212
00:11:57,820 --> 00:11:59,820
Shi Jie and Fu Bi’s alleged revolt.

213
00:12:00,980 --> 00:12:02,300
Your Majesty, do you really think

214
00:12:02,860 --> 00:12:05,820
they’re rebels?

215
00:12:06,860 --> 00:12:08,020
Rebels, once convicted,

216
00:12:08,260 --> 00:12:10,460
will be executed along with their clansmen.

217
00:12:11,980 --> 00:12:13,140
But Your Majesty didn’t

218
00:12:13,140 --> 00:12:14,340
keep Fu Bi in the Capital

219
00:12:14,780 --> 00:12:16,540
or investigate the slanderer.

220
00:12:17,660 --> 00:12:19,100
When proposals are flooding in,

221
00:12:19,620 --> 00:12:21,140
targeting Fan Zhongyan and Du Yan

222
00:12:21,580 --> 00:12:23,620
with Su Shunqin and Wang Yirou,

223
00:12:23,940 --> 00:12:25,380
Your Majesty remained silent.

224
00:12:26,260 --> 00:12:27,220
All the court officials,

225
00:12:27,540 --> 00:12:28,820
other than Wang Gongchen

226
00:12:28,980 --> 00:12:31,180
who held personal grudges
against Su Shunqin and Ouyang Xiu,

227
00:12:31,940 --> 00:12:32,860
are attacking the reform

228
00:12:32,940 --> 00:12:34,260
by attacking them

229
00:12:35,020 --> 00:12:35,940
and attempting to terminate it

230
00:12:36,380 --> 00:12:37,900
by framing them.

231
00:12:38,580 --> 00:12:39,820
Your Majesty, endangering them

232
00:12:40,220 --> 00:12:41,740
is endangering the reform.

233
00:12:46,140 --> 00:12:47,100
Yes.

234
00:12:50,180 --> 00:12:51,900
The reform downsizes officials,

235
00:12:52,700 --> 00:12:54,820
upgrades education and official-selecting systems

236
00:12:55,300 --> 00:12:56,420
and reduces honorary titles,

237
00:12:57,180 --> 00:12:58,460
which harms

238
00:12:58,460 --> 00:12:59,420
some officials’ interests.

239
00:13:00,460 --> 00:13:02,940
Those who suffer losses are in rage.

240
00:13:03,660 --> 00:13:05,380
They’re eager to

241
00:13:05,420 --> 00:13:06,740
and trying every means

242
00:13:06,740 --> 00:13:08,580
to halt the reform.

243
00:13:13,180 --> 00:13:14,740
Did you realize their intention

244
00:13:15,060 --> 00:13:16,980
when Shi Jie and Fu Bi

245
00:13:16,980 --> 00:13:17,820
were said to be rebels

246
00:13:18,340 --> 00:13:19,500
or when other officials

247
00:13:19,500 --> 00:13:20,780
demanded severe punishments

248
00:13:20,780 --> 00:13:22,220
on Su Shunqin and Wang Yirou?

249
00:13:22,660 --> 00:13:23,540
Or

250
00:13:23,540 --> 00:13:25,900
you didn’t realize it until Du Yan

251
00:13:26,300 --> 00:13:27,900
and Fan Zhongyan were implicated?

252
00:13:31,380 --> 00:13:35,180
I’ve known it for long.

253
00:13:36,460 --> 00:13:37,180
But...

254
00:13:37,620 --> 00:13:38,580
But you believed

255
00:13:38,860 --> 00:13:40,140
as long as the reform

256
00:13:40,140 --> 00:13:41,140
was in the national and public interests,

257
00:13:41,420 --> 00:13:43,180
whether the ultimate result

258
00:13:43,180 --> 00:13:44,460
came out as expected or not,

259
00:13:44,620 --> 00:13:46,860
I’d support the reform to the end.

260
00:13:48,540 --> 00:13:49,660
As long as officials leading the reform

261
00:13:49,660 --> 00:13:51,340
were loyal and dedicated,

262
00:13:51,580 --> 00:13:52,940
I’d still empower you

263
00:13:52,940 --> 00:13:54,660
regardless of others’ disagreements.

264
00:13:58,860 --> 00:14:00,860
So Fan Zhongyan was being too stubborn

265
00:14:01,300 --> 00:14:02,700
to be lenient

266
00:14:03,860 --> 00:14:06,180
or to adjust the policies

267
00:14:06,460 --> 00:14:07,820
to the situation.

268
00:14:09,300 --> 00:14:11,500
Ouyang Xiu offended Wang Gongchen,

269
00:14:11,980 --> 00:14:13,860
who’s honest and upright,

270
00:14:13,860 --> 00:14:14,740
as he pleased.

271
00:14:15,940 --> 00:14:17,380
Other than mediating their problems,

272
00:14:17,740 --> 00:14:20,460
he wrote boldly about the Clique of Gentlemen.

273
00:14:22,060 --> 00:14:24,420
What’s worse, Su Shunqin practically

274
00:14:24,860 --> 00:14:26,340
handed his faults to his enemies

275
00:14:26,340 --> 00:14:27,220
on a plate.

276
00:14:28,860 --> 00:14:29,660
You believed

277
00:14:30,860 --> 00:14:31,980
what hinders the reform was

278
00:14:31,980 --> 00:14:33,580
the battle between the honest and the wicked,

279
00:14:34,220 --> 00:14:35,940
the talented and the mediocre,

280
00:14:36,140 --> 00:14:38,380
so you disdained to compromise

281
00:14:38,380 --> 00:14:39,580
and insisted on being yourselves

282
00:14:39,580 --> 00:14:40,780
and showing off your talents.

283
00:14:42,060 --> 00:14:43,220
I didn’t have any disdain.

284
00:14:43,780 --> 00:14:44,780
You didn’t,

285
00:14:45,340 --> 00:14:46,300
but Han Qi,

286
00:14:46,500 --> 00:14:48,140
can you make them

287
00:14:48,140 --> 00:14:49,500
put their self-esteem and stubbornness behind

288
00:14:49,580 --> 00:14:50,740
and focus on their duty first?

289
00:14:54,820 --> 00:14:55,660
I can’t.

290
00:14:57,740 --> 00:14:59,380
Neither can I

291
00:14:59,900 --> 00:15:02,780
leash all the mediocre and wicked.

292
00:15:09,740 --> 00:15:12,060
That’s what happened.

293
00:15:13,340 --> 00:15:15,460
That day, I took a handkerchief

294
00:15:15,460 --> 00:15:17,820
from the closet to wipe princess’s face.

295
00:15:18,580 --> 00:15:19,300
Then

296
00:15:19,460 --> 00:15:22,740
I stuffed it in my clothes.

297
00:15:24,980 --> 00:15:26,020
While hiding

298
00:15:26,020 --> 00:15:28,940
in the wood charcoal carriage,

299
00:15:29,780 --> 00:15:30,940
I kept thinking about

300
00:15:30,940 --> 00:15:32,460
princess’s look that day.

301
00:15:34,020 --> 00:15:36,820
Her lips were blue and she was breathless,

302
00:15:41,260 --> 00:15:42,500
similar to the last time

303
00:15:43,060 --> 00:15:43,980
when Aunt Jia

304
00:15:44,540 --> 00:15:47,500
carried her back.

305
00:15:48,740 --> 00:15:51,300
Back then, the Imperial Physician said

306
00:15:53,380 --> 00:15:55,300
she was allergic to flower powder.

307
00:16:09,180 --> 00:16:11,900
The room she went into when playing hide-and-seek

308
00:16:12,860 --> 00:16:14,740
was one of the maids’

309
00:16:14,940 --> 00:16:17,220
who washes and scents clothes.

310
00:16:22,580 --> 00:16:23,540
Which maid?

311
00:16:25,980 --> 00:16:28,300
Maid...Maid Xu,

312
00:16:29,460 --> 00:16:30,540
Xu Lantiao.

313
00:16:38,820 --> 00:16:40,020
The reform isn’t wrong

314
00:16:40,820 --> 00:16:41,740
but it’s done by the wrong people.

315
00:16:43,620 --> 00:16:45,340
There’s no right or wrong policy

316
00:16:45,940 --> 00:16:47,900
but whether it’s suitable for the majority or not.

317
00:16:49,140 --> 00:16:50,140
At that time,

318
00:16:50,740 --> 00:16:52,700
the excess of officials and corruption

319
00:16:53,380 --> 00:16:55,340
must be stopped,

320
00:16:56,180 --> 00:16:57,700
so new officials were empowered to lead the reform.

321
00:16:58,660 --> 00:16:59,740
Your Majesty already

322
00:17:00,660 --> 00:17:01,980
set the limit to it,

323
00:17:02,860 --> 00:17:03,780
but once we reached it,

324
00:17:04,940 --> 00:17:06,340
we insisted on going forward.

325
00:17:07,580 --> 00:17:08,900
You allowed it

326
00:17:09,940 --> 00:17:11,700
in spite of your concerns.

327
00:17:14,140 --> 00:17:14,900
Unfortunately,

328
00:17:16,380 --> 00:17:17,860
we weren’t unable

329
00:17:17,860 --> 00:17:19,500
to smooth the way

330
00:17:20,740 --> 00:17:22,460
but made it even bumpier.

331
00:17:24,060 --> 00:17:26,100
The excess and corruption are chronic diseases

332
00:17:27,780 --> 00:17:29,940
just like father’s and my heart diseases.

333
00:17:31,860 --> 00:17:33,220
When the condition was critical,

334
00:17:33,940 --> 00:17:36,140
strong medicine was prescribed.

335
00:17:36,620 --> 00:17:37,700
When the condition became stable,

336
00:17:38,260 --> 00:17:40,500
it couldn’t be used anymore to eradicate

337
00:17:41,380 --> 00:17:44,300
the disease in order to protect other organs.

338
00:17:46,660 --> 00:17:47,460
Your Majesty...

339
00:17:51,340 --> 00:17:52,740
Please take care of yourself.

340
00:17:53,660 --> 00:17:56,700
You look emaciated.

341
00:18:02,740 --> 00:18:03,540
Have a safe trip.

342
00:18:04,660 --> 00:18:05,460
Once you arrive in Yangzhou,

343
00:18:05,820 --> 00:18:07,380
don’t forget to send me proposals regularly.

344
00:18:08,380 --> 00:18:09,580
If there’s fresh news,

345
00:18:09,580 --> 00:18:10,660
fun stories,

346
00:18:10,660 --> 00:18:11,700
or anything interesting,

347
00:18:12,180 --> 00:18:13,460
you can let me know.

348
00:18:16,460 --> 00:18:18,580
I’m always busy with work,

349
00:18:19,620 --> 00:18:20,900
but I often feel

350
00:18:22,780 --> 00:18:23,580
bored.

351
00:18:36,980 --> 00:18:37,980
It’s better

352
00:18:38,620 --> 00:18:39,980
to let me tell you in person

353
00:18:40,620 --> 00:18:41,620
when I come back.

354
00:18:47,300 --> 00:18:48,420
I understand what Your Majesty said,

355
00:18:49,580 --> 00:18:50,780
and I’ll be able to come back.

356
00:18:58,140 --> 00:18:58,820
Go ahead.

357
00:19:00,300 --> 00:19:01,180
I’ve kept

358
00:19:01,180 --> 00:19:02,660
some new Drag Ball Tea for you.

359
00:19:03,260 --> 00:19:06,060
Liaozi will bring it to you later.

360
00:19:09,500 --> 00:19:10,340
Thank you, Your Majesty.

361
00:19:14,740 --> 00:19:19,900
= Imperial Physician Zhao’s Mansion =

362
00:19:21,540 --> 00:19:24,500
This is paper mulberry flower
and castor bean powder.

363
00:19:25,980 --> 00:19:28,780
Why would someone use it to scent handkerchiefs?

364
00:19:29,380 --> 00:19:30,700
It’s wrong.

365
00:19:37,260 --> 00:19:38,180
You shouldn’t

366
00:19:38,740 --> 00:19:39,820
use flower powder

367
00:19:39,820 --> 00:19:41,100
on your underclothes.

368
00:19:41,540 --> 00:19:43,420
These two kinds of powder are too strong.

369
00:19:43,940 --> 00:19:45,060
After smelling it,

370
00:19:45,380 --> 00:19:47,380
some may have runny eyes and nose like me,

371
00:19:47,860 --> 00:19:49,700
and some may cough and pant.

372
00:19:50,140 --> 00:19:51,420
If people’s skin is in contact with it,

373
00:19:51,980 --> 00:19:53,860
they may feel itchy

374
00:19:54,340 --> 00:19:55,500
and develop rashes.

375
00:19:59,700 --> 00:20:00,420
Thank you.

376
00:20:00,940 --> 00:20:01,860
Good day.

377
00:20:06,500 --> 00:20:10,020
= Luo’s Silk Store =

378
00:20:10,020 --> 00:20:12,100
You must be new to our store.

379
00:20:12,140 --> 00:20:13,340
Feel free to look around.

380
00:20:13,580 --> 00:20:15,060
We have newly arrived silk from Hangzhou

381
00:20:15,180 --> 00:20:15,940
- and Su... - Sir,

382
00:20:16,660 --> 00:20:17,660
are your garments

383
00:20:17,740 --> 00:20:18,860
all scented?

384
00:20:19,300 --> 00:20:20,100
Of course!

385
00:20:20,660 --> 00:20:23,100
Did you use flower powder?

386
00:20:23,420 --> 00:20:24,260
Flower powder?

387
00:20:25,140 --> 00:20:26,740
No one would use that on fabrics.

388
00:20:28,940 --> 00:20:29,700
Thank you.

389
00:20:48,740 --> 00:20:49,580
Madam,

390
00:20:50,260 --> 00:20:52,820
it’s time to take your medicine.

391
00:20:59,540 --> 00:21:01,900
His Majesty promoted you to Chief of Styling,

392
00:21:02,620 --> 00:21:03,620
Combing Stewardess.

393
00:21:05,940 --> 00:21:07,740
You’re no longer

394
00:21:07,740 --> 00:21:09,020
a maid at my place.

395
00:21:10,940 --> 00:21:12,340
You don’t need to serve me anymore.

396
00:21:14,780 --> 00:21:16,540
His Majesty only promoted me

397
00:21:17,340 --> 00:21:18,860
because of you, madam.

398
00:21:21,220 --> 00:21:23,220
I know very well

399
00:21:24,060 --> 00:21:25,140
whom I’m in debt to.

400
00:21:26,940 --> 00:21:27,860
Besides,

401
00:21:28,260 --> 00:21:31,180
His Majesty asked me to take care of you

402
00:21:31,900 --> 00:21:33,020
and spent more time with you.

403
00:21:34,740 --> 00:21:35,900
You’re the only one

404
00:21:36,620 --> 00:21:38,020
he adores.

405
00:21:39,180 --> 00:21:40,660
You should get better soon.

406
00:21:41,340 --> 00:21:42,620
Whoever you like

407
00:21:43,420 --> 00:21:44,700
and are loyal to you

408
00:21:45,540 --> 00:21:47,300
will be promoted by His Majesty.

409
00:21:50,020 --> 00:21:51,100
Come here.

410
00:21:57,060 --> 00:21:59,700
Please take the medicine first.

411
00:22:00,500 --> 00:22:03,020
I prepared pine nut and date cakes for you.

412
00:22:03,980 --> 00:22:04,900
Finish the medicine first,

413
00:22:05,260 --> 00:22:06,420
and then have a cake.

414
00:22:06,860 --> 00:22:08,860
The bitterness will be gone.

415
00:22:10,660 --> 00:22:13,340
His Majesty told me that himself.

416
00:22:14,260 --> 00:22:16,460
As busy as he is,

417
00:22:17,380 --> 00:22:20,180
he loves you wholeheartedly.

418
00:22:21,220 --> 00:22:22,740
Only if you recover

419
00:22:23,340 --> 00:22:24,780
will he be relieved.

420
00:22:34,540 --> 00:22:35,900
Do you want to be a concubine?

421
00:22:45,740 --> 00:22:47,020
Every woman in this palace

422
00:22:48,020 --> 00:22:49,820
dreams of being His Majesty’s woman

423
00:22:50,980 --> 00:22:52,340
and having his children.

424
00:22:54,060 --> 00:22:56,940
But it’s no secret

425
00:22:57,460 --> 00:22:59,860
that His Majesty only loves you.

426
00:23:06,060 --> 00:23:06,940
Give me the bowl.

427
00:23:35,180 --> 00:23:35,860
Yes.

428
00:23:37,260 --> 00:23:38,380
From now on,

429
00:23:40,020 --> 00:23:41,740
you can serve me during dinner.

430
00:23:47,740 --> 00:23:48,500
Huaiji,

431
00:23:49,580 --> 00:23:53,500
do you remember Shi Jie at the
Directorate of Education?

432
00:23:55,660 --> 00:23:56,420
I do.

433
00:23:57,660 --> 00:23:58,740
He impressed me.

434
00:24:00,340 --> 00:24:02,700
Princess once recited

435
00:24:03,020 --> 00:24:04,820
one of his articles to me.

436
00:24:06,260 --> 00:24:07,820
She doesn’t like

437
00:24:07,820 --> 00:24:09,300
reciting long poems or articles

438
00:24:10,260 --> 00:24:11,860
but she remembered

439
00:24:12,420 --> 00:24:13,820
every word Mr. Shi wrote

440
00:24:13,820 --> 00:24:14,660
in that piece.

441
00:24:16,380 --> 00:24:17,860
Other than reciting it,

442
00:24:19,020 --> 00:24:20,100
she even wrote it down afterwards.

443
00:24:21,780 --> 00:24:24,660
Ode to Imperial Virtue?

444
00:24:30,140 --> 00:24:31,740
Huirou only likes that article

445
00:24:32,220 --> 00:24:33,260
because it praises

446
00:24:33,580 --> 00:24:36,060
her father

447
00:24:36,060 --> 00:24:37,740
from the title.

448
00:24:41,020 --> 00:24:42,140
She’s too young

449
00:24:42,860 --> 00:24:44,700
to judge the quality of such works

450
00:24:46,260 --> 00:24:48,420
or understand

451
00:24:49,500 --> 00:24:51,420
Shi Jie’s aspiration.

452
00:24:54,340 --> 00:24:57,780
As the sun rises, the gate of the palace opens.

453
00:24:58,740 --> 00:25:02,260
Respect the loyal and punish the wicked.

454
00:25:03,260 --> 00:25:06,020
Voice is so loud that it can shake the earth

455
00:25:07,020 --> 00:25:10,500
and resonate with heaven.

456
00:25:11,980 --> 00:25:14,740
Court officials fulfill their duties diligently.

457
00:25:15,060 --> 00:25:17,940
Enemies are in awe,

458
00:25:18,460 --> 00:25:20,820
spreading Your Majesty’s might widely.

459
00:25:21,700 --> 00:25:25,500
They surrender themselves and pay tributes.

460
00:25:26,700 --> 00:25:30,940
Your Majesty’s one move can discipline officials,

461
00:25:31,580 --> 00:25:36,220
intimidate the powerful and conquer the enemies.

462
00:25:38,140 --> 00:25:44,100
Long live, Your Majesty!

463
00:25:48,900 --> 00:25:50,060
What Huirou doesn’t know is

464
00:25:50,500 --> 00:25:51,660
Shi Jie

465
00:25:51,940 --> 00:25:54,100
wasn’t extolling my achievements

466
00:25:55,540 --> 00:25:56,940
but was describing

467
00:25:57,420 --> 00:25:59,300
what he’s longing for.

468
00:26:01,540 --> 00:26:03,540
What he portrayed

469
00:26:03,860 --> 00:26:05,420
wasn’t the state under my reign

470
00:26:06,020 --> 00:26:08,740
but the ideal world he imagined.

471
00:26:12,140 --> 00:26:14,540
Your Majesty, you do like Mr. Shi.

472
00:26:17,780 --> 00:26:20,620
Shi Jie is erudite and straightforward.

473
00:26:20,860 --> 00:26:22,220
I adore him.

474
00:26:23,540 --> 00:26:26,660
I also cherish Mr. Yan’s insight,

475
00:26:26,780 --> 00:26:28,380
Fan Zhongyan’s honesty,

476
00:26:28,580 --> 00:26:29,780
Fu Bi’s loyalty,

477
00:26:30,500 --> 00:26:33,540
Ouyang Xiu’s and Su Shunqin’s talents

478
00:26:33,540 --> 00:26:34,700
and boldness.

479
00:26:34,980 --> 00:26:37,940
But what I love the most

480
00:26:39,460 --> 00:26:40,500
is what Shi Jie descried

481
00:26:41,140 --> 00:26:43,540
in his article

482
00:26:45,460 --> 00:26:47,220
that all officials are loyal and talented.

483
00:26:47,420 --> 00:26:48,500
Enemies all surrender themselves.

484
00:26:48,620 --> 00:26:50,500
People are living a well-off life.

485
00:26:53,700 --> 00:26:54,900
When I was young,

486
00:26:55,780 --> 00:26:58,420
I studied tirelessly in and out of court every day

487
00:26:59,340 --> 00:27:01,180
in hope of

488
00:27:01,820 --> 00:27:03,180
creating such a world for everyone

489
00:27:03,540 --> 00:27:06,300
once I took charge.

490
00:27:12,540 --> 00:27:15,020
But gradually, I’ve realized

491
00:27:16,540 --> 00:27:17,580
that I can’t.

492
00:27:20,580 --> 00:27:22,020
I’ve tried my best

493
00:27:23,540 --> 00:27:25,060
but can barely

494
00:27:25,980 --> 00:27:27,300
balance the court

495
00:27:29,060 --> 00:27:30,420
and bring peace

496
00:27:32,380 --> 00:27:33,940
to the masses.

497
00:27:48,150 --> 00:27:52,830
= 1047 A.D. =
♪ When my bang just grew out ♪

498
00:27:52,830 --> 00:27:56,630
♪ We played games together outside the gate ♪

499
00:27:56,630 --> 00:27:58,000
Mr. Liang.

500
00:27:58,010 --> 00:27:59,730
♪ You rode a toy horse ♪

501
00:27:59,750 --> 00:28:00,600
This way, please.

502
00:28:02,260 --> 00:28:03,420
This ditty is perfect for the occasion.

503
00:28:04,300 --> 00:28:06,820
Today is The Thirteenth Prince
and Miss Gao’s wedding.

504
00:28:07,220 --> 00:28:07,980
Look at them.

505
00:28:07,980 --> 00:28:09,580
One is His Majesty’s adopted son

506
00:28:09,580 --> 00:28:11,300
while the other is the Empress’s adopted daughter.

507
00:28:11,540 --> 00:28:13,100
They grew up together in the palace.

508
00:28:14,140 --> 00:28:16,220
Aren’t they childhood sweethearts?

509
00:28:17,860 --> 00:28:20,020
What a perfect couple!

510
00:28:20,660 --> 00:28:21,300
Of course!

511
00:28:28,180 --> 00:28:33,300
= Imperial Street =

512
00:28:33,470 --> 00:28:38,030
♪ Facing the wall, gazing at the dark corner ♪

513
00:28:38,030 --> 00:28:41,600
♪ Dare not look back or respond to your calling ♪

514
00:28:43,540 --> 00:28:44,340
Mr. Zhang.

515
00:28:47,140 --> 00:28:48,740
Since officials came last month

516
00:28:48,740 --> 00:28:49,980
to check everyone’s identity,

517
00:28:50,260 --> 00:28:52,260
this place has been under constant watch.

518
00:28:53,020 --> 00:28:54,780
Luckily, the business isn’t affected.

519
00:28:54,940 --> 00:28:55,700
I assume

520
00:28:55,700 --> 00:28:57,100
they know you also invested in this restaurant.

521
00:29:04,500 --> 00:29:05,260
Mr. Zhang,

522
00:29:06,860 --> 00:29:08,140
are they there because of that girl?

523
00:29:10,060 --> 00:29:11,060
How is she?

524
00:29:12,260 --> 00:29:13,700
It’s been two years.

525
00:29:13,700 --> 00:29:14,460
How come...

526
00:29:22,980 --> 00:29:23,780
Mr. Zhang,

527
00:29:24,700 --> 00:29:26,580
when mother found her,

528
00:29:26,580 --> 00:29:28,300
she was weak and could hardly breathe.

529
00:29:28,340 --> 00:29:29,420
We saved her.

530
00:29:30,020 --> 00:29:31,140
If she

531
00:29:31,740 --> 00:29:33,500
didn’t do anything wrong,

532
00:29:34,060 --> 00:29:35,420
please spare

533
00:29:37,220 --> 00:29:38,820
that poor girl’s life.

534
00:29:49,780 --> 00:29:51,860
His Majesty’s son is marrying the
Empress’s daughter.

535
00:29:52,180 --> 00:29:53,460
The street is packed

536
00:29:53,460 --> 00:29:54,380
for this marriage alliance!

537
00:29:55,180 --> 00:29:55,790
If there’s nothing else

538
00:29:55,790 --> 00:29:56,980
you need,

539
00:29:56,980 --> 00:29:58,460
I’d like to join the crowd.

540
00:30:03,020 --> 00:30:03,820
Good day.

541
00:30:14,660 --> 00:30:18,300
Marriage alliance.

542
00:30:21,180 --> 00:30:22,620
Why aren’t you taking the soup?

543
00:30:23,380 --> 00:30:25,380
It’s good for your health.

544
00:30:28,260 --> 00:30:29,660
You look worried

545
00:30:30,180 --> 00:30:31,540
when you ask me to take it

546
00:30:32,860 --> 00:30:34,620
because you know how terrible it is

547
00:30:35,260 --> 00:30:36,540
to have this herbal soup every day.

548
00:30:37,980 --> 00:30:38,780
Are you afraid

549
00:30:40,340 --> 00:30:42,460
that I’ll force you to take it?

550
00:30:46,660 --> 00:30:49,260
You must be joking.

551
00:30:50,580 --> 00:30:51,700
Do you know

552
00:30:51,820 --> 00:30:53,340
what this soup is cooked with?

553
00:30:53,860 --> 00:30:56,100
There are decade-old ginseng, dried scallops,

554
00:30:56,300 --> 00:30:58,540
chicken and mutton.

555
00:30:59,260 --> 00:31:00,340
His Majesty bestowed

556
00:31:00,340 --> 00:31:01,540
all those ingredients to you.

557
00:31:01,860 --> 00:31:03,020
You want me to have it?

558
00:31:03,020 --> 00:31:04,220
Are you trying to kill me?

559
00:31:06,980 --> 00:31:08,700
Take this while it’s hot.

560
00:31:18,980 --> 00:31:21,700
Lantiao is a disappointment.

561
00:31:22,860 --> 00:31:25,500
I don’t think His Majesty likes her.

562
00:31:28,340 --> 00:31:29,940
Do you think it’s easy

563
00:31:30,340 --> 00:31:31,340
to win his heart?

564
00:31:32,980 --> 00:31:34,180
I see your point.

565
00:31:35,820 --> 00:31:36,780
But

566
00:31:38,540 --> 00:31:40,580
she’s been allowed

567
00:31:40,580 --> 00:31:41,540
to serve His Majesty

568
00:31:41,540 --> 00:31:42,500
for over a year.

569
00:31:43,140 --> 00:31:44,220
I checked with her.

570
00:31:44,980 --> 00:31:48,020
His Majesty did sleep with her

571
00:31:48,740 --> 00:31:52,180
but there’s no good news yet.

572
00:31:54,260 --> 00:31:55,300
There’s nothing we can do.

573
00:31:56,660 --> 00:31:58,060
Hasn’t the Empress

574
00:31:59,220 --> 00:32:00,540
been like that for over a decade?

575
00:32:03,740 --> 00:32:04,780
The thing is,

576
00:32:04,940 --> 00:32:06,700
His Majesty lost his own son,

577
00:32:07,340 --> 00:32:09,980
so he adopted the Thirteenth Prince.

578
00:32:10,260 --> 00:32:12,100
The Empress raised him

579
00:32:13,140 --> 00:32:16,940
and he’s marrying her adopted daughter

580
00:32:16,980 --> 00:32:17,780
who’s actually

581
00:32:17,860 --> 00:32:19,580
her niece by blood.

582
00:32:19,860 --> 00:32:20,620
I mean...

583
00:32:21,140 --> 00:32:22,380
They dare revolt?

584
00:32:25,180 --> 00:32:26,620
Of course not.

585
00:32:27,420 --> 00:32:28,300
But

586
00:32:30,540 --> 00:32:32,700
His Majesty is 14 years older than you.

587
00:32:33,460 --> 00:32:34,380
If...

588
00:32:39,180 --> 00:32:42,340
He’ll protect me as long as he’s here.

589
00:32:44,060 --> 00:32:45,180
If he’s gone,

590
00:32:47,740 --> 00:32:48,820
I see no reason

591
00:32:49,580 --> 00:32:50,660
to continue staying here.

592
00:33:03,580 --> 00:33:04,820
Osmanthus candy you made

593
00:33:04,820 --> 00:33:06,060
is always my favorite.

594
00:33:06,220 --> 00:33:07,140
Others’ aren’t

595
00:33:07,140 --> 00:33:08,100
as good as yours.

596
00:33:09,300 --> 00:33:10,220
I’ve been making this

597
00:33:10,220 --> 00:33:11,220
since I was eight.

598
00:33:11,780 --> 00:33:13,020
I do have some tips.

599
00:33:17,380 --> 00:33:19,860
Zongshi and Taotao are finally getting married.

600
00:33:21,380 --> 00:33:23,220
I still remember

601
00:33:23,380 --> 00:33:25,900
how close they were

602
00:33:26,340 --> 00:33:27,380
when they were little.

603
00:33:27,380 --> 00:33:28,460
Even Huirou envied them.

604
00:33:29,340 --> 00:33:31,700
Now, they’re officially a couple.

605
00:33:32,620 --> 00:33:34,460
I’m having mixed feelings, too.

606
00:33:35,140 --> 00:33:36,700
When they were still little,

607
00:33:37,740 --> 00:33:38,700
they were always together.

608
00:33:39,060 --> 00:33:40,180
I teased Zongshi

609
00:33:40,340 --> 00:33:42,460
that if he wanted to marry the Empress’s niece.

610
00:33:44,940 --> 00:33:46,580
Back then, he was afraid of me

611
00:33:46,660 --> 00:33:47,900
and was dull and quiet.

612
00:33:47,980 --> 00:33:50,220
But he knelt and thanked me immediately.

613
00:33:53,300 --> 00:33:54,580
I watched him

614
00:33:54,580 --> 00:33:56,020
grow up.

615
00:33:56,860 --> 00:33:58,100
He has a big heart

616
00:33:58,340 --> 00:34:00,340
and loves Taotao wholeheartedly.

617
00:34:01,940 --> 00:34:03,580
Taotao is lucky

618
00:34:04,020 --> 00:34:05,460
to have such a great husband.

619
00:34:12,700 --> 00:34:13,540
Don’t worry.

620
00:34:13,900 --> 00:34:15,220
Although you aren’t as lucky as her,

621
00:34:15,340 --> 00:34:16,620
our daughter

622
00:34:16,780 --> 00:34:18,220
will be married

623
00:34:18,220 --> 00:34:19,100
to a man

624
00:34:19,100 --> 00:34:20,260
who also loves her wholeheartedly.

625
00:34:20,340 --> 00:34:21,300
I didn’t mean...

626
00:34:21,300 --> 00:34:22,940
It’s late. You should rest.

627
00:34:26,580 --> 00:34:27,820
Is Huirou still at the Empress’s chamber?

628
00:34:28,300 --> 00:34:29,020
Yes.

629
00:34:29,260 --> 00:34:30,700
She’ll be back later.

630
00:34:31,100 --> 00:34:32,180
She’s grown up

631
00:34:32,860 --> 00:34:34,100
and is studying hard.

632
00:34:34,260 --> 00:34:35,500
She always visits Her Highness

633
00:34:35,500 --> 00:34:36,820
to study poems and classics

634
00:34:37,020 --> 00:34:38,420
and comes back

635
00:34:38,420 --> 00:34:39,660
before bedtime, yawning.

636
00:34:43,700 --> 00:34:45,420
She’s...

637
00:34:48,740 --> 00:34:49,940
I’ve judged

638
00:34:50,220 --> 00:34:51,540
possible candidates for her marriage

639
00:34:51,700 --> 00:34:53,140
over and over.

640
00:34:53,460 --> 00:34:54,460
There’s one name

641
00:34:55,300 --> 00:34:56,900
in my mind for long.

642
00:34:58,420 --> 00:34:59,140
Alright.

643
00:34:59,860 --> 00:35:02,260
When Zongshi comes back

644
00:35:02,260 --> 00:35:03,420
to pay respects with his wife,

645
00:35:03,660 --> 00:35:05,100
we can discuss it in detail

646
00:35:05,260 --> 00:35:06,380
whether he’s good enough for Huirou.

647
00:35:07,700 --> 00:35:08,540
Good night.

648
00:35:14,780 --> 00:35:15,580
Princess,

649
00:35:15,580 --> 00:35:17,460
you’ve been studying with Her Highness

650
00:35:17,580 --> 00:35:19,180
these days.

651
00:35:19,460 --> 00:35:20,820
She’s passionate

652
00:35:20,820 --> 00:35:21,940
but you look sleepy.

653
00:35:22,460 --> 00:35:24,180
His Majesty always has dinner

654
00:35:24,180 --> 00:35:25,260
with Madam Miao.

655
00:35:25,460 --> 00:35:26,900
When you’re with Her Highness,

656
00:35:26,900 --> 00:35:28,700
you can’t have dinner with him.

657
00:35:29,060 --> 00:35:30,820
I know father is there with mother,

658
00:35:30,900 --> 00:35:32,540
so I can go stay with Her Highness.

659
00:35:33,780 --> 00:35:35,060
Father once said to me

660
00:35:35,140 --> 00:35:37,180
the deaths of Zuixinglai and my eighth sister

661
00:35:37,300 --> 00:35:38,940
broke mother’s and Madam Zhang’s hearts.

662
00:35:39,300 --> 00:35:40,500
Luckily, mother still has me

663
00:35:40,500 --> 00:35:41,340
to support her.

664
00:35:41,660 --> 00:35:42,740
I can cheer her up

665
00:35:42,740 --> 00:35:44,220
for father.

666
00:35:44,620 --> 00:35:45,380
Later,

667
00:35:45,460 --> 00:35:46,260
I noticed

668
00:35:46,260 --> 00:35:47,580
= Princess Huirou =
father often came to have dinner with mother

669
00:35:47,900 --> 00:35:49,580
and spent the night at Pavilion of Luan.

670
00:35:50,140 --> 00:35:52,140
But he forgot

671
00:35:52,460 --> 00:35:53,980
that Her Highness is also alone.

672
00:36:08,380 --> 00:36:10,140
Zongshi and Taotao

673
00:36:10,140 --> 00:36:11,300
are coming back to pay respects today.

674
00:36:11,780 --> 00:36:12,540
Why am I

675
00:36:12,540 --> 00:36:13,780
dressed up like this?

676
00:36:14,140 --> 00:36:15,900
Her Highness even sent Qiuhe here.

677
00:36:18,940 --> 00:36:20,740
You’ve grown up

678
00:36:20,780 --> 00:36:22,340
and no longer want to see me?

679
00:36:22,980 --> 00:36:25,180
You loved playing games with me

680
00:36:25,180 --> 00:36:26,780
when you were little.

681
00:36:28,500 --> 00:36:29,340
No!

682
00:36:29,820 --> 00:36:30,860
It was you

683
00:36:30,860 --> 00:36:32,020
who were eager

684
00:36:32,260 --> 00:36:33,060
to leave the palace to get married

685
00:36:33,060 --> 00:36:34,460
and abandon Her Highness and me.

686
00:36:37,620 --> 00:36:39,740
All maids have to leave one day.

687
00:36:40,260 --> 00:36:41,380
I wasn’t eager to get married.

688
00:36:45,580 --> 00:36:47,380
Qiuhe is old enough

689
00:36:48,140 --> 00:36:50,780
to build her own family

690
00:36:50,860 --> 00:36:52,180
and have children.

691
00:36:53,780 --> 00:36:57,180
One day, you’ll also leave here

692
00:36:57,460 --> 00:36:59,980
and spend the rest of your life with your husband.

693
00:37:00,740 --> 00:37:01,980
I won’t leave father,

694
00:37:01,980 --> 00:37:03,060
Her Highness and you.

695
00:37:03,940 --> 00:37:05,180
No man

696
00:37:05,620 --> 00:37:06,980
is half as good as father.

697
00:37:07,860 --> 00:37:09,020
Oh, silly.

698
00:37:09,860 --> 00:37:12,340
Husband and father are incomparable.

699
00:37:14,980 --> 00:37:17,900
Perhaps once you see someone today,

700
00:37:19,460 --> 00:37:21,220
you can’t wait to leave.

701
00:37:22,260 --> 00:37:23,300
I don’t want a husband.

702
00:37:23,820 --> 00:37:25,020
I won’t look forward

703
00:37:25,020 --> 00:37:25,860
to leaving the palace.

704
00:37:31,140 --> 00:37:33,460
Are you dressing me up

705
00:37:33,980 --> 00:37:35,260
to pick

706
00:37:35,580 --> 00:37:37,220
a husband for me?

707
00:37:39,780 --> 00:37:41,460
Officer at the Court of Judicial Review,

708
00:37:41,460 --> 00:37:43,300
Teaching Assistant at the Directorate of Education,

709
00:37:43,340 --> 00:37:44,540
Sima Guang pays respects to Your Majesty.

710
00:37:45,620 --> 00:37:46,780
It’s been a while

711
00:37:46,780 --> 00:37:47,980
since you came back to the Capital

712
00:37:47,980 --> 00:37:49,260
to teach at the Directorate of Education.

713
00:37:49,460 --> 00:37:51,260
I finally have time

714
00:37:51,580 --> 00:37:53,500
to discuss literature with you.

715
00:37:54,300 --> 00:37:56,580
You’ve composed

716
00:37:56,660 --> 00:37:58,180
quite a lot of masterpieces these years.

717
00:37:58,900 --> 00:37:59,580
Have a seat.

718
00:38:00,460 --> 00:38:02,500
= Sima Guang, courtesy name Junshi =
I don’t deserve Your Majesty’s compliment.

719
00:38:03,340 --> 00:38:04,420
Don’t be too humble.

720
00:38:05,660 --> 00:38:08,580
I meant to ask you
about this Discourse on Adjustment.

721
00:38:20,900 --> 00:38:23,020
Huaiji, shouldn’t you thank Mr. Sima?

722
00:38:25,420 --> 00:38:26,540
My name is Liang Huaiji.

723
00:38:27,140 --> 00:38:28,900
I once delivered a glazed cup

724
00:38:28,900 --> 00:38:30,020
bestowed by His Majesty to you.

725
00:38:30,860 --> 00:38:31,860
Thank you

726
00:38:32,180 --> 00:38:32,940
for forgiving me

727
00:38:32,940 --> 00:38:34,740
when I failed to keep it intact.

728
00:38:35,900 --> 00:38:36,620
No need to thank me.

729
00:38:37,180 --> 00:38:39,300
You should be more cautious.

730
00:38:39,980 --> 00:38:41,260
No error is allowed

731
00:38:41,980 --> 00:38:44,420
when serving His Majesty.

732
00:38:45,380 --> 00:38:46,700
Thank you for your instruction.

733
00:38:50,140 --> 00:38:52,300
Huaiji is always meticulous.

734
00:38:53,060 --> 00:38:54,020
He’s young,

735
00:38:54,300 --> 00:38:55,940
but more capable

736
00:38:56,220 --> 00:38:58,500
than many experienced senior eunuchs.

737
00:38:59,340 --> 00:39:01,740
Rarest of all, he’s intelligent,

738
00:39:01,780 --> 00:39:03,340
Knowledgeable and

739
00:39:03,820 --> 00:39:04,780
well-versed in poems

740
00:39:05,740 --> 00:39:07,500
and calligraphy.

741
00:39:11,180 --> 00:39:11,940
I think

742
00:39:12,700 --> 00:39:15,180
eunuchs’ duty is to serve Your Majesty.

743
00:39:16,220 --> 00:39:17,300
Having basic knowledge

744
00:39:17,300 --> 00:39:19,740
is enough in their line of duty.

745
00:39:20,500 --> 00:39:21,260
The more they know,

746
00:39:21,820 --> 00:39:23,380
the more they say.

747
00:39:23,860 --> 00:39:25,900
Eunuchs are with Your Majesty all the time.

748
00:39:26,580 --> 00:39:28,060
Their opinions

749
00:39:28,740 --> 00:39:30,700
may affect Your Majesty’s judgment.

750
00:39:34,260 --> 00:39:34,980
Huaiji,

751
00:39:35,420 --> 00:39:38,220
take the two paintings

752
00:39:38,380 --> 00:39:39,500
and new pigment

753
00:39:39,580 --> 00:39:40,860
from my chamber

754
00:39:41,100 --> 00:39:43,180
and bring them to Huirou.

755
00:39:44,780 --> 00:39:45,460
Yes.

756
00:39:52,540 --> 00:39:53,460
This article

757
00:39:53,540 --> 00:39:54,740
was written out of sheer boredom.

758
00:39:54,980 --> 00:39:55,820
It’s not worth to be discussed.

759
00:39:56,380 --> 00:39:57,940
Given my rank,

760
00:39:58,180 --> 00:39:59,820
I seldom have the chance to meet Your Majesty.

761
00:40:00,140 --> 00:40:02,620
Today, I do have a few things to report.

762
00:40:15,300 --> 00:40:16,540
Now that she’s dressed up,

763
00:40:16,660 --> 00:40:17,580
she does

764
00:40:17,580 --> 00:40:18,980
look like an adult.

765
00:40:22,580 --> 00:40:23,620
Madam, princess,

766
00:40:23,940 --> 00:40:25,700
Huaiji came with His Majesty’s gifts for you.

767
00:40:26,020 --> 00:40:27,540
Just now, you were busy,

768
00:40:27,540 --> 00:40:28,700
so he couldn’t come in.

769
00:40:28,740 --> 00:40:30,020
He’s outside, waiting to be summoned.

770
00:40:30,260 --> 00:40:31,580
= Lusi =
Madam, princess,

771
00:40:31,580 --> 00:40:32,740
do you need anything else?

772
00:40:33,340 --> 00:40:34,780
Why didn’t you tell me Huaiji came?

773
00:40:34,940 --> 00:40:36,620
If he could chat with me,

774
00:40:36,860 --> 00:40:38,660
I’d feel less bored when being dolled up.

775
00:40:41,260 --> 00:40:41,860
Huaiji.

776
00:40:41,860 --> 00:40:42,500
Princess.

777
00:40:42,780 --> 00:40:43,940
You haven’t been here for long.

778
00:40:44,740 --> 00:40:45,780
I came a while ago

779
00:40:45,780 --> 00:40:47,260
to see you draw chrysanthemums.

780
00:40:47,700 --> 00:40:48,740
That was ten days ago.

781
00:40:48,780 --> 00:40:50,140
Aren’t ten days long enough?

782
00:40:50,980 --> 00:40:51,660
Huaiji,

783
00:40:51,780 --> 00:40:52,940
Zongshi and Taotao

784
00:40:52,940 --> 00:40:54,500
are coming back to pay respects today.

785
00:40:54,780 --> 00:40:56,660
Her Highness and the guests are at the backyard.

786
00:40:56,900 --> 00:40:58,140
Mother and I are going there, too.

787
00:40:58,820 --> 00:41:00,060
Why don’t you join me?

788
00:41:01,460 --> 00:41:02,300
Yes.

789
00:41:03,500 --> 00:41:05,220
I just said she looked like an adult,

790
00:41:06,100 --> 00:41:07,780
but inside, she’s still a child.

791
00:41:10,100 --> 00:41:11,780
Your Majesty, you are almost 40
and still have no son.

792
00:41:12,420 --> 00:41:14,020
Madam Zhang is enjoying too much favor

793
00:41:14,460 --> 00:41:15,420
while other concubines...

794
00:41:15,420 --> 00:41:16,260
You’ve been speaking nonstop

795
00:41:16,260 --> 00:41:17,380
for over two hours

796
00:41:17,980 --> 00:41:19,420
and listed 14 suggestions.

797
00:41:20,180 --> 00:41:21,380
Every one of them

798
00:41:22,660 --> 00:41:24,740
has been raised more than once

799
00:41:24,900 --> 00:41:26,260
by more than one censor

800
00:41:26,260 --> 00:41:27,780
during the past three years.

801
00:41:28,340 --> 00:41:29,660
There’s nothing new.

802
00:41:29,900 --> 00:41:30,860
Obviously,

803
00:41:30,860 --> 00:41:32,220
they aren’t just my personal opinions.

804
00:41:32,660 --> 00:41:33,540
All officials are concerned

805
00:41:33,820 --> 00:41:35,140
but Your Majesty,

806
00:41:35,140 --> 00:41:36,060
you refuse to take our advice,

807
00:41:36,660 --> 00:41:38,540
so we have no choice

808
00:41:38,540 --> 00:41:39,700
but to repeat suggestions

809
00:41:39,780 --> 00:41:41,140
that aren’t new.

810
00:41:41,540 --> 00:41:42,340
Alright.

811
00:41:45,980 --> 00:41:46,860
I’ve heard enough.

812
00:41:49,220 --> 00:41:54,020
Zongshi is coming back today with his wife.

813
00:41:54,580 --> 00:41:57,020
The Empress and the guests are at the backyard.

814
00:41:57,580 --> 00:41:59,060
I’ll join them later.

815
00:41:59,340 --> 00:42:02,540
Let’s call it a day.

816
00:42:03,820 --> 00:42:05,020
I have one more thing to report.

817
00:42:06,060 --> 00:42:08,620
It’s about the Empress.

818
00:42:12,540 --> 00:42:13,420
The Empress?

819
00:42:15,340 --> 00:42:16,500
You’re impeaching the Empress?

820
00:42:28,300 --> 00:42:29,780
I guess father and Her Highness

821
00:42:29,780 --> 00:42:31,260
are going to pick a husband for me.

822
00:42:33,460 --> 00:42:34,220
Huaiji,

823
00:42:34,660 --> 00:42:36,900
if they decide on the person,

824
00:42:37,260 --> 00:42:38,380
please go out and see

825
00:42:38,860 --> 00:42:40,420
what he looks like.

826
00:42:57,190 --> 00:43:04,190
♪ Memory is the breath of deep sleep ♪

827
00:43:04,750 --> 00:43:11,630
♪ It emerges in every crevice ♪

828
00:43:12,110 --> 00:43:18,470
♪ Shallow dreams
are like copper bells under eaves ♪

829
00:43:18,910 --> 00:43:25,670
♪ Woken up when the wind blows ♪

830
00:43:26,910 --> 00:43:33,710
♪ Fate is predetermined ♪

831
00:43:34,310 --> 00:43:41,070
♪ Struggle to break out of it ♪

832
00:43:41,630 --> 00:43:48,670
♪ Who will battle fate with me ♪

833
00:43:48,670 --> 00:43:55,470
♪ Regardless of the ending ♪

834
00:44:00,350 --> 00:44:03,870
♪ Peach branches shake in the spring breeze ♪

835
00:44:04,070 --> 00:44:07,670
♪ Walls sigh, the wind is silent ♪

836
00:44:07,670 --> 00:44:10,870
♪ The boy beside the wall is unaware of it ♪

837
00:44:10,870 --> 00:44:15,270
♪ He plays with the butterfly, gathering honey ♪

838
00:44:15,270 --> 00:44:18,990
♪ Peach blossoms tell a love story ♪

839
00:44:18,990 --> 00:44:22,550
♪ About a couple who lives happily ♪

840
00:44:22,550 --> 00:44:26,270
♪ Unluckily deep love comes to nowhere ♪

841
00:44:26,270 --> 00:44:32,030
♪ All fated,
drawing Double Happiness in autumn ♪

842
00:44:33,830 --> 00:44:36,950
♪ Peach branches shake in the spring breeze ♪

843
00:44:37,470 --> 00:44:40,830
♪ Walls sigh, the wind is silent ♪

844
00:44:41,070 --> 00:44:44,350
♪ The boy beside the wall is unaware of it ♪

845
00:44:44,350 --> 00:44:48,710
♪ He plays with the butterfly gathering honey ♪

846
00:44:48,710 --> 00:44:51,870
♪ Peach blossoms tell a love story ♪

847
00:44:52,350 --> 00:44:56,030
♪ About a couple who lives happily ♪

848
00:44:56,030 --> 00:44:59,710
♪ Unluckily deep love comes to nowhere ♪

849
00:44:59,710 --> 00:45:06,110
♪ All fated,
drawing Double Happiness in autumn ♪
